{"kanda":6,"sarga":86,"description":"","verses":[{"v":1,"dev":"अथतस्यामवस्थायांलक्ष्मणंरावणानुजः ।परेषामहितंवाक्यमर्थसाधकमब्रवीत्","trans":"Ravana's brother seeing Lakshmana spoke these words of advice to accomplish the task and which is not good for the enemies.","words":[{"d":"अथ","m":"and then"},{"d":"रावणानुजः","m":"Ravana's brother"},{"d":"तस्याम्","m":"them"},{"d":"लक्ष्मणं","m":"Lakshmana अवस्थायाम् tendered"},{"d":"परेषाम्","m":"for enemies"},{"d":"अहितम्","m":"not good"},{"d":"अर्थसाधकम्","m":"to accomplish the task"},{"d":"वाक्यम्","m":"words"},{"d":"अब्रवीत्","m":"spoke"}]},{"v":2,"dev":"यदेतद्राक्षसानीकंमेघश्यामंविलोक्यते ।एतदायोध्यतांशीघ्रंकपिभिपादपायुधैः","trans":"\"The army of Rakshasas looks like a dark cloud and let the monkeys too get engaged to fight swiftly with trees as weapons.\"","words":[{"d":"मेघश्यामम्","m":"dark as cloud"},{"d":"यत्","m":"that which"},{"d":"एतत्","m":"all that"},{"d":"राक्षसानीकम्","m":"army of Rakshasas"},{"d":"विलोक्यते","m":"be engaged"},{"d":"एतत्","m":"all this"},{"d":"पादपायुधैः","m":"trees as weapons"},{"d":"कपिभिः","m":"monkeys too"},{"d":"शीघ्रम्","m":"swiftly"},{"d":"अयोध्यताम्","m":"will get engaged"}]},{"v":3,"dev":"अस्यानीकस्यमहतोभेदनेयतलक्ष्मण ।राक्षसेन्द्रसुतोऽप्यत्रभिन्नेदृश्योभविष्यति","trans":"\"O Lakshmana! Shatter this mighty army of Rakshasas. When it is broken Ravana's son will become visible.\"","words":[{"d":"लक्ष्मण","m":"Lakshmana"},{"d":"महतः","m":"mighty"},{"d":"अस्यअनीकस्य","m":"army of Rakshasas"},{"d":"भेदने","m":"shatter"},{"d":"यत","m":"that which"},{"d":"अत्र","m":"there"},{"d":"भिन्ने","m":"broken"},{"d":"राक्षसेन्द्रसुतोऽपि","m":"the son of Rakshasa king"},{"d":"दृश्यःभविष्यति","m":"will become visible"}]},{"v":4,"dev":"सत्वमिन्द्राशनिप्रख्यैःशरैरवकिरन्परान् ।अभिद्रवाशुयावद्वैनैतत्कर्मसमाप्यते","trans":"\"You have come to attack the enemy. Before he completes his action quickly attack him with the thunderbolt of Indra.\"","words":[{"d":"सः","m":"he"},{"d":"त्वम्","m":"by you"},{"d":"इन्द