ः च","m":"Rakshasas also"},{"d":"समरे","m":"in battle"},{"d":"कपिसैन्यजिघांसवः","m":"to kill monkey army"},{"d":"शितैः","m":"sharp"},{"d":"बाणैः","m":"shafts"},{"d":"असिभिः","m":"swords"},{"d":"शक्तितोमरैः","m":"javelins and lances"},{"d":"उद्यतै:","m":"launched"},{"d":"अभ्यवर्तन्त","m":"attacked"}]},{"v":9,"dev":"स सम्प्रहारस्तुमुलःसञ्जज्ञेकपिरक्षसाम् ।शब्देनमहतालङ्कांनादयन्वैसमन्ततः","trans":"With both the monkeys and Rakshasas mutually striking intensely, the mighty sounds resounded all over Lanka","words":[{"d":"कपिरक्षसाम्","m":"monkeys and Rakshasas"},{"d":"महता","m":"mighty"},{"d":"शब्देन","m":"sounds"},{"d":"लङ्काम्","m":"Lanka"},{"d":"समन्ततः","m":"all over"},{"d":"नादयन्वै","m":"resounded"},{"d":"सः","m":"that"},{"d":"तुमुलः","m":"intense"},{"d":"सम्प्रहारः","m":"mutual striking"},{"d":"सञ्जज्ञे","m":"equipped with"}]},{"v":10,"dev":"शस्त्रश्चविविधाकारैश्शितैर्बाणैश्चपादपैः ।उद्यतैर्गिरिशृङ्गैश्चघोरैराकाशमावृतम्","trans":"The sky was covered with weapons of various shapes, arrows, trees, mountain peaks thrown at each other and were dreadful.","words":[{"d":"विविधाकारैः","m":"various shapes"},{"d":"शस्त्रः","m":"weapons"},{"d":"शितैः","m":"sharp"},{"d":"बाणैश्च","m":"arrows also"},{"d":"पादपैः","m":"trees"},{"d":"उद्यतैः","m":"thrown"},{"d":"घोरैः","m":"dreadful"},{"d":"गिरिशृङ्गैश्च","m":"mountain peaks"},{"d":"आकाशम्","m":"sky"},{"d":"आवृतम्","m":"covered"}]},{"v":11,"dev":"तेराक्षसावानरेषुविकृताननबाहवः ।निवेशयन्तःशस्त्राणिचक्रुस्तेसुमहद्भयम्","trans":"The Rakshasas with disfigured faces and arms, attacked the Vanaras, and their bodies pierced with weapons created great fear in them.","words":[{"d":"विकृताननबाहवः","m":"misshapen faces and arms"},{"d":"तेराक्षसाः","m":"those Rakshasas"},{"d":"वानरेषु","m":"at monkeys"},{"d":"शस्त्राणि","m":"weapons"},{"d":"निवेशयन्तः","m":"pierced in their bodies"},{"d":"ते","m":"in them"},{"d":"सुमहत्","m":"great"},{"d":"भयम्","m":"fear"},{"d":"चक्रुः","m":"created"}]},{"v":12,"dev":"तथैवसकलैर्वृक्षैर्गिरिशृङ्गैश्चवानराः 