rmly fixed"},{"d":"सज्जम्","m":"ready"},{"d":"रथम्","m":"chariot"},{"d":"आरुरोह","m":"ascended"}]},{"v":16,"dev":"स भीमकार्मुकधरःकालमेघसमप्रभ: ।रक्तास्यनयनोकृद्धोमभौमृत्युरिवान्तकः","trans":"Indrajith, armed with a terrific bow and arrows, his body shining like a rainy cloud, with red eyes, angry face, seemed like the spirit of death.","words":[{"d":"भीमकार्मुकशरः","m":"armed with terrific bow and arrows"},{"d":"कालमेघसमप्रभ:","m":"body shining like a rainy cloud"},{"d":"रक्तास्यनयनः","m":"with red eyes"},{"d":"कृद्ध:","m":"angry"},{"d":"सः","m":"he"},{"d":"अन्तकः","m":"like spirit of death"},{"d":"मृत्युरिव","m":"like death"},{"d":"बभौ","m":"seemed"}]},{"v":17,"dev":"दृष्टवैवतुरथस्थंतंपर्यवर्तततद्बलम् ।रक्षसांभीमवेगानांलक्ष्मणेनयुयुत्सताम्","trans":"Seeing Lakshmana prepared for war, the Rakshasa army endowed with speed surrounded him.","words":[{"d":"रथस्थम्","m":"from the chariot"},{"d":"तम्","m":"him"},{"d":"दृष्टवैव","m":"seeing"},{"d":"लक्ष्मणेन","m":"Lakshmana"},{"d":"युयुत्सताम्","m":"prepared for war"},{"d":"भीमवेगानाम्","m":"endowed with terrific speed"},{"d":"रक्षसाम्","m":"Rakshasas"},{"d":"तत् बलम्","m":"his army"},{"d":"पर्यवर्तत","m":"surrounded"}]},{"v":18,"dev":"तस्मिन् कालेतुहनूमानुद्यम्यसुदुरासदम् ।धरणीधरसङ्काशोमहावृक्षमरिन्दमः स राक्षसानांतत्सैन्यंकालाग्निरिवनिर्दहन् ।चकारबहुभिर्वक्षैर्निःसंज्ञंयुधिवानरः","trans":"In the meantime, Hanuman, who resembled a mountain, a tamer of enemies, who is difficult to overpower, taking up huge trees fighting with Rakshasas created havoc like fire at the time of dissolution and went about.","words":[{"d":"तस्मिन् काले","m":"in the meantime"},{"d":"धरणीधरसङ्काशः","m":"who resembled mountain"},{"d":"अरिन्दमः","m":"tamer of enemies"},{"d":"हनुमान्","m":"Hanuman"},{"d":"सुदुरासदम्","m":"difficult to overpower"},{"d":"महावृक्षम्","m":"huge tree"},{"d":"उद्यम्य","m":"taking up"},{"d":"राक्षसानाम्","m":"at Rakshasas"},{"d":"तत्","m":"those"},{"d":"सैन्यम्","m":"army"},{"d":"कालाग्निरिव","m":"like fire at dissolution"}